        <li><strong>Communication:</strong> "They kept me updated after every lesson. I knew exactly where my daughter stood."</li>
        <li><strong>Adult learners:</strong> "Never too old to learn. I got my license at 34 and the instructor made me feel completely comfortable."</li>
      </ul>

